<l>colliya valla vēṉaiya vellān</l>
<l>tēruṅ kālai yurupoṭu civaṇic</l>
<l>cāriyai nilaiyuṅ kaṭappā ṭilavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Words [denoting] direction,</l>
<l>when followed by the seventh-case marker,</l>
<l>will not optionally take the empty-morph [<foreign xml:lang="ta">iṉ</foreign>] ;</l>
<l>there, the ending with the consonant is dropped.</l>
